    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bedspreads made of plain textile squares folded to frame smaller squares of colored or printed textile, the total effect being somewhat like stained glass windows.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000008611/Houck, Quilt Encyclopedia (1991)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sobrecamas hechas de cuadrados de tela lisa doblados para enmarcar pequeños cuadrados de tela de colores o estampada, el efecto total es algo así como ventanas de vitrales.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Beddenspreien vervaardigd uit effen vierkante stukken stof die om kleinere vierkantjes van gekleurd of bedrukt textiel worden gevouwen zodat het geheel wel wat op glas-in-lood ramen lijkt. Geen Nederlands equivalent.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>以摺疊的素面方形布料框住小塊彩色或印花布料，再拼接而成的床單，視覺效果類似彩繪玻璃窗。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
